    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a dream to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for its next big adventure! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin. I\u2019d love to see it go to a great home!",
