      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system for optimized torque across the powerband. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a functional M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The suspension retains its precision with refreshed bushings and McPherson struts, while the braking system utilizes cross-drilled ventilated rotors for consistent thermal management. Though displaying minor aesthetic patina typical of an enthusiast-driven vehicle, the mechanical tolerances remain tight and the throttle response is exceptionally sharp.",
